# Account Deletion Flow

## Endpoint
`DELETE /api/users/{user_id}` — user can only delete own account (`can_edit_user`)

## Backend
1. Check permission: `can_edit_user(user_id)` = is_self or admin
2. Delete subscriptions where others subscribed TO this user
3. Null out question_options.author_id
4. Delete user (CASCADE: user_settings, questions, answers, subscriptions)
5. Commit

## Response
204 No Content on success
